article_title: Seven Gazans reported dead in latest Jabalia attack.
sentence: An  Israeli  operation  at  the  Jabalia  refugee  camp  in  northern  Gaza  has  killed  seven  people  today,  according  to  local  media  and  a  journalist  on  the  ground  speaking  to  the  BBC.

article_title: Seven Gazans reported dead in latest Jabalia attack.
sentence: After  Israeli  forces  ordered  an  evacuation  from  a  school  in  the  centre  of  the  camp,  seven  people  were  reportedly  killed  by  artillery  fire,  with  their  bodies  taken  to  the  Kamal  Adwan  hospital  nearby.

article_title: Seven Gazans reported dead in latest Jabalia attack.
sentence: Yesterday,  one  of  the  most  senior  IDF  soldiers  to  have  died  in  the  past  year  was  killed  near  the  camp.
